Change keystoke repeat rate, The changes aren't applied until you log out and back in. KeyRepeat can't be set between 2 (30 ms) and 1 (15 ms) though.


    defaults write -g InitialKeyRepeat -int 10 # normal minimum is 15 (225 ms)
    defaults write -g KeyRepeat -int 1 # normal minimum is 2 (30 ms)

